title: Swiss couple cycle 10,000 miles to see son compete
text:
Swiss couple cycle 10,000 miles to see son compete 11:28am GMT - 01:57 
A year and 10,000 miles later, a Swiss couple arrived in Pyeongchang last week to watch their son compete in the Winter Olympics. Colette Luke has more. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
